-- Nigeria's Diamond Bank to raise $750 mln fresh capital
-- By Oludare Mayowa
-- Wed Apr 02, 2014 05:27AM EDT
-- None



LAGOS, April 2 (Reuters) - Nigeria's Diamond Bank <DIAMONB.LG> said on Wednesday it will seek shareholders' approval to raise additional capital up to $750 million or its naira equivalent at its general meeting on April 24.

